&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own end-to-end execution of advisor events, including planning, logistics, delivery, and post-event follow-up, ensuring a consistently high standard of quality and detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and manage a calendar of partner-hosted networking events, premium experiences, and community programming tailored to specific advisor segments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate high-level goals into structured plans, timelines, and run-of-show documents that keep multiple concurrent events on track.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design thoughtful, high-value experiences that strengthen advisor engagement and create meaningful connections with partners.&lt;/li&gt;
