&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Director of Agency Management&lt;/strong&gt; to build and operate Fora&#39;s agency business—a new model to support established agencies as well as home-grown focused, specialist agencies operating at Fora. This is a rare opportunity to stand up an entirely new line of business from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
