&lt;li&gt;Build the SOPs and onboarding playbook that get agencies productive fast—including product and Fora-tool adoption,with Sales and the Solutions Architect / ProdOps teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the ongoing account and accountability owner for agencies once they&#39;re on the platform.&lt;/li&gt;
